<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Stretch</title>
  <%- include ../../partials/_head %>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='styles/stretch.min.css'>
</head>
<body class="stretch stretch-cms">
  <%- include ../../partials/_menu %>
  <%- include ../../partials/_stretch-subnav %>
  <main class="wrapper case-study">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content bottom container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Stretch CMS</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Run&nbsp;live&nbsp;online&nbsp;<br />events&nbsp;like&nbsp;a&nbsp;pro</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Live Event CMS</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded purple">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We researched how clients operate in the real world, and created a new system that complements not just what they&rsquo;re already doing, but inspires them to try something new.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded light-black">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Running Live Events&nbsp;<br />Already Takes Work
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            How could we mirror offline processes like scheduling and sales, without saddling organizations with redundant&nbsp;features?
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Custom Content with&nbsp;<br />Critical Context
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            In every use case, we prioritize the right data and workflows, while empowering each organization to make their Portal their&nbsp;own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Research</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block bg-image extra-padded white" data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/section1.png" style="background-position: bottom">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md two-third-lg">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop shadow darker rounded sr-left lazy-ratio" data-width="1544" data-height="904">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/soccer-cup-stats.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile half-md one-third-lg">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h4 class="case-block-heading">The&nbsp;first&nbsp;time and&nbsp;every&nbsp;time</h4>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              The data couldn&rsquo;t be clearer: mobile is where the future of streaming video is headed. For those craving a bigger experience, our fully-flexible UI delivers up to giant, HD&nbsp;screens.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block bg-image extra-padded gray" data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/section2.png" style="background-position: top">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column gutter-bottom-mobile half-md one-third-lg">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h4 class="case-block-heading">Seamless&nbsp;brand extension</h4>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              A thoughtful, consistent approach to typography and color results in full-customization, down to event categories and advertising, that makes every organization look&nbsp;polished.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md two-third-lg">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop shadow dark rounded sr-right lazy-ratio" data-width="1440" data-height="828">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/portal-editor.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/keynote.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block bg-image padded-top light-black" data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/performance-stats-bg.jpg" style="background-position: bottom">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">High priority</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
              We worked with Stretch to introduce a game-changing feature: deep statistics on your events and viewers. Admins now have the power to find out what&rsquo;s working, what&rsquo;s popular, and how they can improve their streams.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop shadow dark rounded sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="788" data-height="936">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/performance-stats.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block extra-padded light-black stretch-wave stretch-cms-power-tools">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="605" data-height="501">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/create-a-highlight.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-left">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h4 class="case-block-heading">Power&nbsp;tools&nbsp; for&nbsp;everyone</h4>
            <p class="case-block-text">
                Whether it&rsquo;s testing a connection or creating a highlight clip, we took the best modern influences and created elegant tools that anyone can pick&nbsp;up.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top purple stretch-cms-features">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right padded-bottom">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Features to-go</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
                We considered every possible context, before, during and after an event. Users can even run a virtual scoreboard from our CMS, no app-install&nbsp;needed. 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile shadow lighter sr-bottom">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/portal.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/cms/musician.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md gray">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Long quote here from Jordan Duvall or another Stretch team member</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md purple">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">Long quote here from Jordan Duvall or another Stretch team member lorem ipsum dolot sit amet. Long quote here from Jordan Duvall or another Stretch team member lorem ipsum dolot sit amet.</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Jordan Duvall, <em>Position, Stretch Live</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <a href="./work/stretch/support" class="block block-link bg-image padded teal" data-normal="./images/work/stretch/systems-bg.jpg">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content container">
            <h4 class="case-block-tagline">Next</h4>
            <h2 class="case-block-heading lg">The System</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text lg">
              A force-multiplying, all-seeing dashboard for the best client support team in&nbsp;the&nbsp;business
            </p>
            <div class="btn btn-box alt">View Case Study</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block gutter-left-mobile half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-right rounded dark shadow sr-right lazy-ratio" data-width="1144" data-height="800">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/systems.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/upfront" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
        <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
        <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
      </div>
      <a href="./work/ijr" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
    </section>

    <%- include ../../partials/_footer %>
  </main>

  <%- include ../../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
